11... Bb7 12. b3 cxb3 13. Nxb3
{ Black is going to have a lot of trouble containing the knight and justifying his weaknesses on the queenside. Keep in mind that we can also shift our focus to the kingside by playing moves like e4 and Ng5 at the right time. }
