Nxd7 Qxd7 12. Ne5 Nxe5 13. Bxe5 Bc5 14. b4 Bb6
{ 14...Bxb4  15.Rb1  The entrance on the 7th rank decides the game. } 15. a4 a6
16. a5 Ba7 17. Qd3
{ We have fixed Black's queenside structure on light squares, and Black will be very uncomfortable defending his position. }
17... Rc3 18. Qd2 O-O 19. Bxf6 gxf6 20. Qh6 Qe7
