11... Re8
{ Black does not want to compromise in the center and goes for a useful waiting move. }
12. h3
{ We reply with the same medicine.   It is worth remembering that if White now plays  12.Nb3  after  12...dxc4  Black will be able to exchange queens. }
12... g6
{ 12...h6  13.cxd5  exd5  14.Nf1  All our pieces are pointing to Black's king. }
