13... Nf6 14. a3 d5
{ Black wants to trade the hostage on b4 for another piece. } 15. Rd1 Qe7 16.
Ne3
{ We will recapture on d5 and Black will still not have solved the problem with the bishop on a5. It will be a constant suffering for Black to make sense of it. }
