{ Now we can afford this move, as a6 can curiously end up being an inaccuracy depending on Black's play. }
10... exd5 11. exd5 b5 12. cxb5 Ne4 13. Nxe4 Rxe4 14. Bg5
{ With a clear advantage, Black's queenside has not developed, and we will continue to gain time by attacking the e4-rook. }
