11. Nbd2 { Our idea is to go Bh6 and Black's development is too slow. } 11...
Qxb2 12. Rfb1 Qa3 13. e4
{ Black has holes on dark squares, lack of development, and a weak king, while all our pieces are active. Black has all the ingredients to cook a great disaster. }
