17... Qe7 18. f4 { Our goal is to take advantage of the exposed queen. } 18...
Ng4
{ 18...Nf7  19.Re1  in this case the queen will not be able to take shelter from our rooks, so with Be6-Rad1 we will generate many annoying discovered attacks. }
