12... Nxe4 13. Nxe4 Bf5
{ Against almost any other mve, our answer will be the same. } 14. b4 cxb4 15.
Rxb4
{ Ideally, we would continue with Bg5 to force Black's ...f6 move. Therefore, our opponent's reaction is logical. }
15... Bxe4 16. Bxe4
