9. Bc4
{ Now that Black has spent a tempo playing ...Bb7, we don't mind losing a tempo to take on b5 with our bishop. In this case, we want to play Nge2. }
9... axb5 10. Bxb5 e6 11. Nge2 exd5 12. exd5 Na6
{ Black's aim is to increase the pressure against our d5-pawn. } 13. O-O
