6... Bg4 7. Be2 Bxf3 8. Bxf3 Nge7 9. O-O Bg7 10. Ra2
{ Black will be able to take on e5, but after b4 or b3 our rook will become very active. There will be a lot of pressure along the d-file and on top of that we still have the bishop pair. }
