Be2 Bb7 8. a4
{ This motif works beautifully here. We'll get the c4 square and weaken Black's queenside. }
8... b4 9. Nbd2
{ In this structures with dxc4 - b5 plans, having the knight on c3 is sometimes the cause of trouble as b5-b4 is always on the menu and we get less pressure from the c file. }
