8... Nd5
{ A very tempting move. Black hopes to play ...Qh4+ and take on d4 if we go Bd2. }
9. Bd2 Qh4+ 10. g3 Qxd4 11. e4 Nxc3 12. bxc3 Bxc3 13. Ra2
{ We will continue with  13...--  14.Qc1!  and Black can do nothing to avoid losing material. }
