15. h5
{ Enabling quite some options such as Rh4 and Nh4 and threatening both ...h6 and ...g6 pushes. The a8-h1 diagonal is very tasty for our interests. }
15... Nd7 { Black can now develop the knight without being afraid of Nh4. } 16.
h6
{ Now Black has to face the unpleasant reality of the pressure on g7 and not being able to play a desirable move like ...g6. }
