10. b3 c5 11. Ne5 { Exploiting Black's lack of development. } 11... Bxe4 12.
Qb5+ Qxb5 13. Bxb5+ Nbd7 14. Bf4
{ And we managed to transpose to a variation that is winning for White. } *

